  "help.recognition.title": "Recognition modes",
  "help.recognition.body": "Local Parakeet uses the built-in microphone capture, VAD, and local AI runtime. Web Speech opens a separate Google Chrome worker window and streams Web Speech API results back to this app. The experimental mode tries a newer audio-track path and should be treated as a compatibility test.",
